		<title type="html"><![CDATA[La importancia de reunirse]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://tarsacom.com/blog/index.php/2011/05/26/421/" />
		<id>http://tarsacom.com/blog/?p=421</id>
